  contradictoryClaimId: CL001
  explanationText: "Theo's receipt shows he paid at the caf\xE9 at 3:05 PM, yet the
    gallery alarm triggered at 3:08 PM \u2014 only 3 minutes later. The caf\xE9 is
    a minimum 38 minutes away. He could not have been at both locations. His alibi
    is physically impossible."
